{"tid":726114,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"明報記者遭警方圍毆投訴不成立　","createTime":"2018-07-02T06:35:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-02T12:04:58.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"de204daa5388b03a809ba122b1bc495e291cae78","tid":726114,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T06:35:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180702/s00001/7fea9d0da2565fa77f2d18ebe033660f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180702%2Fs00001%2F7fea9d0da2565fa77f2d18ebe033660f.jpg&h=db7ad9a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《明報》一名記者2016年初採訪旺角衝突期間遭警員襲擊，隨即報案並獲轉介至投訴警察課。事隔逾兩年，投訴警察課終於回覆投訴人，明報職工協會指調查有結果，相關指控分別列為「無法追查」或「無法完全證明屬實」。<br />\n<br />\n明報職工協會對於警察投訴課的調查結果感到憤怒及強烈不滿，要求警方及監警會重新覆核決定，並會研究其他可能的法律追究行動。<br />\n<br />\n事緣《明報》一名記者2016年2月10日凌晨在一架停泊的雙層巴士上層拍攝，遭警員驅趕下車。當記者表明身分按警員指示離開巴士，即被巴士外的多名警員用盾牌按在地上，遭警棍打後頸及腳踢。記者當時有佩戴記者證，同時高聲表明身分，但警員沒有停止，打了記者一會才肯放開。記者經檢查證實頭部後方受傷流血，要縫一針，手指亦有擦損，大腿感痛楚。據《蘋果日報》拍得片段所見，明報記者倒地後，多名軍裝及便裝探員衝前，不顧記者已倒地，拿起警棍亂棍揮擊，維持約15秒。<br />\n<br />\n事隔超過兩年，投訴警察課回覆投訴人稱已全面調查事件，包括查問有關人員、證人、相關紀錄及報告，其中一項「毆打」及一項「行為不當」指控，因「不能確定被投訴的警務人員身分」，故列作「無法追查」。<br />\n<br />\n另一項涉及記者遭多名警員「毆打」指控，投訴警察課認為「有若干證據支持，但未能充分證明投訴屬實」，故列作「無法完全證明屬實」。不過，投訴課同時指出，會將相關事件記錄及通知有關人員作出適當紀律行動。<br />\n<br />\n投訴警察課稱監警會同意調查結果，重申「警務處長一向堅決確保屬下人員執行職務時，要處事得當，以禮待人」。投訴警察課又說，若不滿意有關分類，可於30天內要求覆核。"},{"pid":"dc9ee19d1ce8c72527db84bd0b3939dab3217ebf","tid":726114,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T06:36:08.000Z","msg":"<strong>明報記者投訴內容及投訴警察課回應如下：<br />\n<br />\n（一）毆打（無法追查）</strong><br />\n<br />\n投訴：兩至三名警員在巴士樓梯間抓住記者頸部及將記者推出巴士。<br />\n<br />\n回應：沒有充分證據證明投訴及確定被投訴警員身分，故列作無法追查。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>（二）毆打（無法完全證明屬實）</strong><br />\n<br />\n投訴：被6至8名警員用腳踢及用硬物毆打。<br />\n<br />\n回應：有若干證據支持，但未能充分證明投訴屬實，故列作「無法完全證名屬實」。記錄事件並通知有關人員作適當紀律行動，提升警隊服務質素，以更能符合廣大市民期望。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>（三）行為不當（無法追查）</strong><br />\n<br />\n投訴：警員沒有依照警察通例配合傳媒工作。<br />\n<br />\n回應：沒有充分證據證明投訴及確定被投訴警員身分，故列作無法追查。"},{"pid":"ca02fd91bc70c4853c9fd32c922ad822e57dd455","tid":726114,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T06:36:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180702/s00001/1530505756545\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180702%2Fs00001%2F1530505756545&d=P5OUB97JOs26NiDkPvkxSP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=bdef4658\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180702%2Fs00001%2F1530505756545&h=7d759a69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180702/s00001/1530505756545</a>"},{"pid":"1997e37294b38485b79e0eddc64b41fc2e59afd7","tid":726114,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T06:58:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c3e26e45e7208ff84f35f57aeeb6054d5ec8e54","tid":726114,"uid":23786,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T07:10:04.000Z","msg":"有證據就直接民事告一哥叫佢賠錢，仲投訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之前先有單賠十八萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dde2a2ac8f4b7ba259762cfca0d226b22751f93","tid":726114,"uid":81575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T07:21:12.000Z","msg":"監警會啦"},{"pid":"d8a9d5d66a47546421471cc926bd5335eb69ce55","tid":726114,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c3e26e45e7208ff84f35f57aeeb6054d5ec8e54","tid":726114,"uid":23786,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T07:10:04.000Z","msg":"有證據就直接民事告一哥叫佢賠錢，仲投訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之前先有單賠十八萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T07:22:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就黎香港要好似贏國咁裝哂cctv, 唔好信現場d所謂證人, 全部用視像睇"},{"pid":"3eb5a8232b06355eb11f685cc68c30d6173b4929","tid":726114,"uid":190540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T07:24:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dbdc7456b879e5fd49d45b030cde75fbd25d7455","tid":726114,"uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T07:27:35.000Z","msg":"投訴成立才是新聞"},{"pid":"34ccae8d7cc23353286576f8f792d7a4a8a0c759","tid":726114,"uid":119895,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T07:29:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.android-hk.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/81ee73e5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.android-hk.com%2Fwordpress%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F03%2F81ee73e5.jpg&h=57c65da5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8f0fad2357bac424a95ea3bbb140a12f1c9b1c13","tid":726114,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T07:33:40.000Z","msg":"記時會發生記者圍嘔差佬投訴不成立？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bca1ebcf4187c61c540456ad9b5176ed44491afa","tid":726114,"uid":125026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T08:04:07.000Z","msg":"監警會連做下樣都廢事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a91663bfe3c75b12fa67ce2a52e6cb09d40d6e8","tid":726114,"uid":33864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T08:08:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b58c94b182f997e3654727688ba901f164a5bd89","tid":726114,"uid":37869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T08:12:39.000Z","msg":"應該學美國咁<br />\n警察每次一出警署就要帶住個攝影機放係身上<br />\n警察有責任證明自己冇傷害過原告人<br />\n否則就判原告人勝訴"},{"pid":"75e08d41272ce762495f7886f921e84f5c2e3205","tid":726114,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T08:27:22.000Z","msg":"圍毆係以禮待人<br />\n果然係慈母<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15711216e032e3bee37104b7b9c1be4fbce7f871","tid":726114,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T12:03:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f190239df5b3a8877680d9c3e4b8983fb28e1a75","tid":726114,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T12:04:58.000Z","msg":"黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}